add_create_rule_motion

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_create_rule_motion -  This method puts a new rule up for voting.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_create_rule_motion(string area,
int type,
string text,
string creator)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^area%^RESET%^ - the area for the rule to be voted on in
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of the rules
%^BOLD%^text%^RESET%^ - the text associated with the new rule
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/inherit/player_council.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method puts a new rule up for voting.  It is first placed into
the hands of the magistrates, then into the hands of the players.
.EP

